<p>All email communications with you require your consent, either explicit or inferred. The emails you receive contain details regarding unsubscribing from our data base.</p>
 
 
<h3>Security</h3>
<p>Puntacana Resort & Club operates secure data networks, protected by the industry standard firewall and password protection systems, to guard against the loss, misuse or alteration of information under the company’s control. Our security and privacy policies are periodically reviewed and enhanced as necessary and only authorized individuals have access to the information provided by customers.</p>
 
 
<h3>Complaints and Enquiries</h3>
<p>Please contact our Marketing department by email <span id="cloake95a595e9c38ec42aa8f6dcbdf4ad9c0">This email address is being protected from spambots. You need JavaScript enabled to view it.</span><script type='text/javascript'>
